ht:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e3cee666-17f3-470f-81e0-c7a034b0ed78\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>최대 사이즈</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5031cd7f-d18b-4c12-bc27-34bea968857e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 펼쳤을 때 전개도가 약 A3 안에 들어갈 때</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e1def349-d119-4383-bba4-43c30283a821\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6b24722a-fcee-4a2d-9bcd-1ff9f5080be4\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>인쇄 색상</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-34a95dff-8815-486a-9c97-12cb85038306\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 인쇄 칼라 4도 인쇄</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-af412906-320c-4359-99b2-4f3c6737ffa5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-bbad4d82-c86f-4bd2-98d5-3f7f082a6c1d\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>최소 수량</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ea7b607e-2abf-40cb-928d-b0153b7a8077\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 2장</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7c57c0c3-3435-4ff6-8306-d685633b7536\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f7460239-7188-474c-b32e-70527cd27e52\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-504d675d-a657-49c6-8dc8-e9ddeb4988da\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 양면테이프 접착, 칼선 디지털 커팅</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dcffb931-148b-4aca-a89e-42b916fdef98\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0ba659dc-56a0-4cb5-93aa-236599559351\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>납